CLIPPERS at WARRIORS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | October 21, 2021

Led by Stephen Curry’s 45 PTS (8-13 3pt FG) and 10 REB, the Golden State Warriors defeated the LA Clippers, 115-113. Draymond Green added 10 PTS, 6 REB and 7 AST for the Warriors in the victory, while Paul George tallied a team-high 29 PTS and 11 REB, along with 6 AST for the Clippers in the losing effort. The Warriors improve to 2-0 on the season, while the Clippers fall to 0-1.
